            comments="Looks good.")
public interface UnivariateScalarFunction
extends Evaluator<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Double>, ScalarFunction<java.lang.Double>
    Simple interface that describes a function that maps the reals to the reals, has a Double to Double and double to double. It is recommended that a UnivariateScalarFunction implement CloneableSerializable, though it is not required.
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Kevin R. Dixon
